title: 820-3462 Liquid Damage - High fan > Boot Chime > Shutdown
message: Ppbus_g3h is one of the power rails on the board , you can find the voltage on the rail using a multi meter. Chime . Aka the sound emitted by a healthy macbook right after powering on
